snippet.textDisplay:
Those talking about corona virus must be just came from YT recommended and not the real RA fans, real fans will talk about stability of each unit, unit model design etc., all topic about the game.

Let's me clarify, the modder's chinese name “日冕”  is the sun's corona, not the corona virus. Just google translate it and you will get the "corona" as the translation result too.
Definition for those not understand: The rarefied gaseous envelope of the sun and other stars. The sun's corona is normally visible only during a total solar eclipse when it is seen as an irregularly shaped pearly glow surrounding the darkened disk of the moon.

For those talking about corona virus here, you're at the wrong channel and just get the F- out from this channel !
